    p Cards are simple way to present data in a boxed container. Default Cards does not apply any style to the cards and you are free to use utility classes to create cards of different styles.

    h2 Cards With Border
    p Use the <code>.border</code> or <code>.border-dark</code> utility classes to apply border to the card.
    .code-example
      .code-output
        .grid.gutters.mt-medium
          .col
            .card.border
              .card-header
                .h3 Card Title
                .text-muted Card subtitle
              .card-body Card Body with light border.
              .card-footer
                a.button.button-primary Buy Now
          .col
            .card.bg-light.border-dark
              .card-header
                .h3 Card Title
                .text-muted Card subtitle
              .card-body Card Body with light background and dark border.
              .card-footer
                a.button.button-primary Buy Now
