    h2 Cards With Images
    p Use <code>.card-image</code> class to add images to card. You can give a padding if needed using <code>.px</code> utility class. Note that we have also used <code>d-flex</code> utility class to make the cards equal height.
    .code-example
      .code-output
        .grid.gutters.mt-medium
          .col.col-4.d-flex
            .card.shadow
              .card-image
                img(src="/img/stock/space1.jpg")
              .card-header
                .h3 Card Title
                .text-muted Card subtitle
              .card-body Card Body with Image on top.
              .card-footer
                a.button.button-primary Buy Now
          .col.col-4.d-flex
            .card.shadow
              .card-header
                .h3 Card Title
                .text-muted Card subtitle
              .card-image
                img(src="/img/stock/space2.jpg")
              .card-body Card Body with full width image in body.
              .card-footer
                a.button.button-primary Buy Now
